{"TopicDetails": {"type": 0, "ccm2Id": 31093048, "cftId": 0, "identifier": "ISFB-2017-AG-ESUR", "title": "Call for proposals for EU Member States to support the improvement of border surveillance", "publicationDateLong": 1517270400000, "callIdentifier": "ISFB-2017-AG-ESUR", "callTitle": "Call for proposals for EU Member States to support the improvement of border surveillance", "callccm2Id": 31093049, "allowPartnerSearch": true, "workProgrammepart": {"id": 266563, "ccm_id": 31093311, "wp_part": "ISFB-2017", "wp_year": "ISFB-2017", "wp_title": "Internal Security Fund Borders and Visa ", "wp_website": "https://ec.europa.eu/home-affairs/financing/fundings/security-and-safeguarding-liberties/internal-security-fund-borders_en", "wp_document": "http://ec.europa.eu/research/participants/data/ref/other_eu_prog/home/wp/isfb-awp-2017_en.pdf"}, "frameworkProgramme": {"id": 31077833, "abbreviation": "ISFB", "description": "Internal Security Fund Borders and Visa"}, "programmeDivision": [{"id": 31077834, "abbreviation": "ISFB-1", "description": "ISFB-1"}, {"id": 31077835, "abbreviation": "ISFB-1-1", "description": "Border management"}], "topicMGAs": [], "tags": ["EUROSUR", "border"], "sme": false, "actions": [{"status": {"id": 31094503, "abbreviation": "Closed", "description": "Closed"}, "types": [{"typeOfAction": "ISFB-AG ISFB Action Grant", "typeOfMGA": []}], "plannedOpeningDate": "30 January 2018", "submissionProcedure": {"id": 31094504, "abbreviation": "single-stage", "description": "single-stage"}, "deadlineDates": ["20 March 2018"]}], "latestInfos": [], "budgetOverviewJSONItem": {"budgetTopicActionMap": {"3234119": [{"action": "ISFB-2017-AG-ESUR - ISFB-AG ISFB Action Grant", "plannedOpeningDate": "30 January 2018", "deadlineModel": "single-stage", "deadlineDates": ["20 March 2018"], "budgetYearMap": {"2017": 4500000}, "budgetTopicActionMap": {}}]}, "budgetYearsColumns": ["2017"]}, "description": "<SPAN class=\"topicdescriptionkind\">Scope</SPAN>:<p>The present Call for Proposals aims at funding projects on the topic of supporting the improvement of border surveillance by enhancing cooperation between Member States in the framework of EUROSUR, including, whenever appropriate, cooperation with third countries (especially neighbouring countries).</p><p>Project applications submitted under the present Call for Proposals must address at least one of the following priorities:</p><ul level=\"0\"><li>Collection and exchange of information on the European Situational Picture and the Common Pre-frontier Intelligence Picture of EUROSUR, in order to prevent irregular departures of migrants and for early identification of smugglers, as foreseen in the EU Action Plan against migrant smuggling.</li><li>Support to Member States capacities to detect and track small vessels.</li><li>Cooperation between neighbouring Member States and of Member States with third (mostly neighbouring) countries in the framework of EUROSUR.</li> </ul>\n", "conditions": "<p><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:115%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#003366;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp; Eligible countries: </span></b><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nline-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; All EU Member States </span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nline-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nline-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">and the Schengen Associated Countries</span> with the exception of United Kingdom and Ireland. </span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>DEFAULT TEXT</p>\n<p><strong>2. </strong>A<strong>dmissibility requirements and eligibility criteria</strong>: See sections 5 and 6 of the<a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/research/participants/data/ref/other_eu_prog/home/wp-call/isfb-call-proposals-ag-esur-17_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"> Call document</a>.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\n<p><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:115%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#003366;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">3. Indicative timetable for evaluation and grant agreement:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-GB;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"> described in section 3 of the <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/research/participants/data/ref/other_eu_prog/home/wp-call/isfb-call-proposals-ag-esur-17_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Call document</a>.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#003366;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">4.&nbsp;&nbsp; Proposal templates and model grant agreements (MGA):</span></b></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#003366;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/research/participants/data/ref/other_eu_prog/home/tpl/pt/amif-isfb-isfp_call-pt-17_en.pdf\" t