 Model Grant Agreement</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"><br />\r\n&nbsp; </span></span></span></p>\n<p>Members of consortium are required to conclude a consortium agreement prior to the signature of the grant agreement.</p>\n<p><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:115%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#003366;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">5.&nbsp;&nbsp; Additional documents:<br />\r\n</span></b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nline-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\"><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/home-affairs/sites/homeaffairs/files/revised_annual_work_programme_for_union_actions_isf_2017.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">ISFB Work Programme</span></span></a></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/research/participants/data/ref/other_eu_prog/home/legal/isfb-legalbasis_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">ISFB establishment act</a></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/PDF/?uri=CELEX:0201